lead_paragraph: Quade Cooper's Olympic dreams were dashed on Thursday when the former Wallabies flyhalf was ruled out of selection for Australia's Rugby Sevens side at this year's Rio Games.

headline.print_headline: Australia Rule Out Cooper's Sevens Selection for Rio
